Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:27.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:84188,87191}Grandfather doesn't\Nunderstand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:29.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87191,89235}Miss, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:30.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:89235,90153}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:35.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:92280,95533}You want to go to John's place, right?\NHere, you're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103374,105168}Don't open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105168,107003}No! Open it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:54.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113134,114469}What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114469,116596}Go, Lassie! To John's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:03.35,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:118097,123353}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,310)}Unknown Places!\NSearch For Lassie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125480,128650}Do you understand\Nwhat you have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128650,130443}Yes. Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:17.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131486,137367}My entire family is made of fools. I was hoping\Nthat at least you would have some brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:22.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138326,142872}Let us assume that this dog really knows\Nwhere Greenall Bridge is and is headed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:27.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142872,147001}We are in Scotland now.\NIt is four hundred miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147001,148795}This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:33.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148795,153007}I was finally able to acquire a decent dog,\Nand you sentenced it to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153007,155468}Acquire? That's just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:39.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156469,159430}You can't be sure if John\Nfails to fulfill his promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159430,162183}and you're already thinking\Nthat Lassie is all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162725,165478}You told me that\Nyou had a manly agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165478,168690}Did you ever stop to think what would\Nhappen if they did find new deposits?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170108,171776}You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:56.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171776,176114}So why did John and Lassie\Nhad to put up with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:58.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176114,178991}They didn't really want to be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179992,183788}In the end, all you wanted\Nwas to own Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185373,186999}Priscilla…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.62,0:03:10.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187625,190211}The road ahead of Lassie\Nwill be steep and dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:13.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190211,193923}Not all people she's going to meet\Nare going to be like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:19.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193923,199220}willing to understand and love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201139,204976}You better pray\Nfor Lassie's good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212150,213985}Look at that, Willy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215319,217488}A pretty nice dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217488,219490}It's a Rough Collie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219490,222034}What do you think it's doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222034,223494}Uh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228458,229709}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229709,232295}Wait there, yes, just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232295,234380}It's fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234380,236424}Good. Don't run anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:04:00.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236424,240178}No need to fear us.\NJust stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241512,243556}Very well. Good doggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244140,245141}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245725,247143}– Willie!\N– Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248019,249771}Damn! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250062,253274}It must be a runaway\Nfrom the Duke's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:17.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254275,257111}Damn it!\NWhere is it hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:21.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257111,261783}We'll get a good bonus\Nif we catch that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262074,265620}Hell, I'm sure it's hiding\Nhere somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265620,266662}Ah! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268956,270458}No, not with the stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270458,272210}If we hurt it, it'll be worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272210,273669}But we can't catch it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274462,275129}Lemme think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278007,280551}What? A message? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281177,282136}Who is it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283262,284555}Guess who.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:47.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285181,287225}Stop teasing and just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288476,289227}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291479,293523}Priscilla Radling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293523,296651}Ah, it's from Scotland!\NIt's from Priscilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302698,304742}Did she write about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:05.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304742,305993}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:08.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305993,308538}She escaped from\Ntheir manor in Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308704,309914}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309914,311290}When she fled the manor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311666,314460}she ran straight south.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314460,317463}There are people who saw\NLassie heading south.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327223,328182}To the south…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328641,330268}That doesn't mean anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332812,335648}No, if she goes south,\Nshe'll reach Yorkshire, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335648,339068}Lassie wants to return home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339068,340278}Just a moment, John…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340278,342363}All right! I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342363,343698}Just a moment, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344198,346200}We must find coal,\None way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:51.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346784,351497}I will do everything so that Lassie doesn't\Nhave to go anywhere when she returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352915,354500}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:17.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376188,377815}How's it going, master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:21.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377815,381694}The famous Loch Ness Monster\Nwill simply not come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381694,383487}A monster would be really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383487,386240}That's just another bleak landscape.\NA bit boring, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386240,387325}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387325,390202}I found something\Ninteresting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390202,393331}You mean the dog over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393331,396208}It's been sitting there forever,\Nstaring beyond horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:42.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397418,402757}Perhaps there's something precious\Nto that dog on the other side of the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402757,404675}You're quite\Na romantic, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424195,425780}What is it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426530,429325}Looks to me like\Nit wants to cross the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429325,430284}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439335,441087}What a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442713,445675}What's there on the other side\Nthat it went across the lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445675,447385}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:31.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447385,451305}All I know it must be something\Nvery dear to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451305,452390}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:13.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491220,493597}So I went and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493597,495975}"here, you can have one".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:19.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496475,499979}I had to be specific, otherwise\NJimmy would eat the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:21.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500271,501439}You're too funny, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510448,511991}I bet in the end\NJimmy ate everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511991,513159}Yeah, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540603,541854}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542605,544607}It's okay, you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544607,546317}They're just leftovers, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:07.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546317,547902}Here. Have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553115,555326}What a good-mannered guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555326,556702}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.41,0:09:21.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557411,561332}{\i1}John, I have published\Nan ad in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:27.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562208,567129}{\i1}Anyone who sees a beautiful brown\NCollie dog may contact me for a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:36.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575346,576555}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579850,583395}Yes. So it matched the description\Npublished in the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583395,585439}Where is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585439,586524}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:51.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587650,591737}{\i1}I noticed that Lassie\Nwas heading straight south.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591737,595449}{\i1}To be specific, she was\Nheading straight towards London.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596450,597660}{\i1}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597660,602248}{\i1}Lassie continues\Nheading to your town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:08.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603457,608838}{\i1}The picture I sent is from Loch Ness in Scotland.\NShe was standing in that exact spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610798,612383}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630568,632486}No! It'll bite us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:57.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656844,657803}Got ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:03.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660723,663809}Caught you, you dirty dog!
Comment: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:07.64,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:667646,667646}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676614,678782}Damn that mutt,\Nnot knowing when to give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:24.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683913,684663}Stop struggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694548,696300}What's with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696300,697843}It calmed down all of the sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698719,700346}Well, let's get it in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715945,717196}Oh? There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:09.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727039,729750}Unbelievable.\NIt fled into the court!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731794,734588}The defendant\Ncan call his first witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736966,740344}Oh, my. Is that your witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742888,745057}I terribly apologize.\NWe'll catch it in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:32.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750562,752231}Good heavens! What a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788100,789476}Dad, quick! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789476,792187}Damn, it's here\Nto attack the sheep again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794940,796108}Look, there's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802031,803907}– Did I hit it?\N– Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824845,827389}Maybe it was\Njust your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827389,828515}It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828515,831727}I'm certain I heard some noise\Ncoming from right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831727,833937}It sounded like a hurt animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833937,836899}Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843364,845532}Oh, that's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:06.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845532,846909}What did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846909,849495}Come and see.\NIt's a big dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849495,853040}Who did this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853040,854917}You poor thing…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858462,861173}This wound was\Ninflicted with a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861173,863675}Who would shoot at\Nsuch a miserable dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:29.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864343,869056}Maybe it was Tommy.\NHe came to repair the radio last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:34.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869056,874395}I heard that they had a problem with a dog\Nthat assaulted their flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875479,878690}So this dog was\Nattacking their sheep?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880651,882694}No, that's not right, Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:46.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882945,886990}This dog cannot attack sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:51.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886990,891995}Is it your woman's intuition again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:55.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891995,895457}Sometimes things are\Ndifferent than it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:01.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895999,901630}I know you agree with me,\Notherwise you wouldn't let it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901630,903757}Hmm, maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923235,924445}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924445,925904}Are you still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925904,927197}The breakfast is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927197,929450}Okay, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930951,934496}Lassie was way ahead of you.\NShe wants to play already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934496,935789}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935789,937499}Maybe she's full of energy now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937499,939334}but she's always sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:43.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940586,943046}How are you feeling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:46.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943046,946216}I brought you some warm milk.\NHere, have a sip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946842,950220}You feed her our milk?\NNo wonder the bottles are all empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:54.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951138,954224}You can have a breakfast\Nwithout milk from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954766,956226}Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956226,959396}What Englishman\Ndrinks tea without milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:02.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959396,962232}Looks like I'm\Nthe only one complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:09.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966111,969114}Oh, you can stand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:13.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971283,973869}It's been four days\Nsince we found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:16.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973869,976371}Darling, close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976371,978332}Purcell will come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:23.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979917,983962}Purcell, I know you can walk again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983962,986340}But you need to be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988425,989593}Come to think of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:33.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990219,993013}Ever since Danny went to war,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:37.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993013,997684}there's been only the two of us\Nliving in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:41.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997684,1001230}Darling, you treat Purcell\Nlike she was human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002022,1004608}You're the one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005359,1006693}She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:53.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006693,1013492}With her, we'll never have to worry that she'll\Ngo to Belgium for war and never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013492,1014493}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015827,1018747}{\i1}This picture was taken\Na week ago in a court.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:02.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019248,1022000}{\i1}After that there weren't\Nany sightings of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:06.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022459,1026004}{\i1}But I'm sure she's in good health\Nand continues her journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027381,1028507}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029174,1031510}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:25.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045065,1045816}Purcell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049152,1050988}Don't open the door, Dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:37.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053240,1057035}Purcell. You can't go out yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057035,1059204}Your wound hasn't healed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060205,1061707}Purcell…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061707,1064543}Please, don't make us sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:53.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066253,1073427}We'd be very sad if you got sick.\NJust a little longer, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076054,1077055}I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078056,1080434}Okay, darling. It's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083061,1084062}Today as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:07.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084062,1087316}Yes, she does that\Nat three o'clock, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.23,0:18:11.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088233,1091820}Specifically at three o'clock…\NWhat could she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101288,1103415}I still look out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103415,1104625}Listen, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:30.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104625,1110339}Lassie will come home in no time, then she'll\Nbe sitting right there, at 3 o'clock sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111340,1111798}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115010,1116637}And that, as they say, is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:41.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118263,1121308}Right, Purcell?\NIt was a funny story, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:06.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1144206,1146875}Purcell… you poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:18.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154883,1158220}Today's oatmeal\Nis a little hardened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:22.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161973,1162933}Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163767,1166103}Hm? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166103,1169898}I have a feeling that\Nshe might not be happy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171274,1173402}Your woman's intuition again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173402,1175320}It's not just a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175320,1177823}I'm fairly certain\Nyou've noticed it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:41.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179157,1181576}You're worrying too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:47.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181576,1187582}Even if her eyes are a bit teary,\Nit's just that something got in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:52.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187582,1192546}Frankly she reminds me\Nof the times when Danny was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192546,1194339}I feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:59.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195006,1199553}But why don't you let her\Ngo out for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:04.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199553,1204766}When Danny was little, you loved\Nwalking with him in the forest so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205600,1208603}But Purcell has hurt her leg—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:11.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208603,1211940}You know very well that\Nher injury has become much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:18.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212774,1218905}Aren't you just afraid that once you let\Nher out, she won't be coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:24.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220657,1224453}She seems to be traveling\Nto a certain place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224453,1227873}Our house is just a stop\Nto rest for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:33.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228498,1233128}She is clever and grateful, so she\Nwon't go anywhere until we let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233795,1236798}We may be hurting her\Nwithout knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239176,1241178}But it will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:44.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241178,1244556}We have lived\Na long and fruitful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245348,1246308}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:50.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246308,1250437}It's okay to go back to living\Nwith just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:56.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250437,1256109}Even before Purcell came,\Nyou and I were always happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256109,1258028}Yes. You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268997,1270540}Come here, Purcell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:14.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270957,1274544}No… You have\Na different name, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:20.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277547,1280926}If you have to go,\Nnow's the time, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1283887,1285806}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292354,1293980}It's okay. You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293980,1296066}Be happy, wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:38.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296066,1298318}Yes. That is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306326,1308245}We made the right decision, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308245,1309579}Yes. We did.
